name: Korean Air 747 Business Class and 777 First Class Seoul to Jeju
description:
Let's fly the planet's busiest air route with Korean Air from Seoul's Gimpo Airport to Jeju!

Join me on the second floor of a Boeing 747 from Seoul to Jeju and in First Class on a 777 on the way back! Meanwhile, you'll see a bit of Jeju, too!

Curious about Jeju? Check out this page:

https://OutOfPlace.com/Jeju/
